{"tid":2203134,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【害人不淺】美國海關查獲 50萬副中国假N95口罩","createTime":"2020-09-15T06:32:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-15T07:00:21.000Z","uid":293677,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7ac7a9cc25adca9f7440cdf4498ee356b4bafb72","tid":2203134,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T06:32:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/09/15/phpvZHPAI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F09%2F15%2FphpvZHPAI.jpg&h=ecbda60f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2020/09/15 11:10<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕<span class=\"red\">美國海關及邊境保衛局（CBP）14日表示，10日在芝加哥歐海爾國際機場扣押50萬副來自中國的假N95口罩，估計價值超過300萬美元（約新台幣8842萬元），這些口罩不符合美國政府規定的過濾標準。</span><br />\n<br />\nCBP聲明指出，<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><ins>這批口罩來自中國深圳</ins></span></span>，原本要被送往新澤西州馬納拉潘市（Manalapan）的一間公司，10日抵達芝加哥歐海爾國際機場時被海關扣押。CBP將其中30副N95口罩送至西維吉尼亞州的疾病管制與預防中心（CDC）檢測辦公室進行抽檢，發現其中10%的口罩過濾能力低於95%。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">CBP官員表示，這些口罩不符合CDC規定的安全標準，讓公眾面臨風險，危害所有人的健康和福祉。</span></span><br />\n<br />\nN95口罩是指符合美國規定的NIOSH空氣過濾等級標準「N95」級別、可阻擋95%直徑0.3微米以上的非油性顆粒的口罩，其最大特點是可以預防由患者體液或血液飛濺引起的飛沫傳播。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3291977\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3291977&d=ulKCtXgG4rwmRR8qyGKIuXljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=be9ddcfa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3291977&h=7669d3ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3291977</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span class=\"limegreen\">中国製造 害人不淺</span>"},{"pid":"5bbfe06b90ab9c3648aa01d2939e63e4857f48fa","tid":2203134,"uid":9435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T06:44:51.000Z","msg":"終國反擊了"},{"pid":"780ff6de96bf1ddc9165474bec5a5a37ee40152f","tid":2203134,"uid":89517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T07:00:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}